Bharat Petroleum Issues Tender to Buy Crude Oil for October

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-08-16T14:21:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/bharat-petroleum-issues-tender-to-buy-crude-oil-for-september.html
Bharat Petroleum Corp.,  India ’s
second-largest state-run oil refiner, is seeking to buy West and
North African crude cargoes for loading in the first half of
October, according to documents received by Bloomberg News.  Last month, the company bought 1 million barrels each of
Angolan Nemba crude from Sonangol SA and Nigerian Agbami from
Chevron Corp.  Details of the Mumbai-based refiner’s requirements are:  To contact the reporter on this story:
